1. The project uses Yarn as its package manager.
2. The common folder contains shared types and utilities used by both frontend and backend.
3. The server folder contains the backend implementation, using the @tarpit framework, github url is https://github.com/isatiso/node-tarpit
4. The ui folder contains the frontend implementation, using Angular.
5. The deploy folder is used for building Docker images.
6. 所有函数名以及变量名应该用下划线命名方式。